<P>
   URINAL (Undated) _ The last time a urinal was the center of
attention, it was signed by Marcel Duchamp and hanging upside down
in an show of avant-garde art. Today, the urinal has taken its
stand alongside the bidet and the working fireplace as the latest
must-have in the well-appointed bathroom suite. By Julie Iovine.
</P>
