<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-27 10:14 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3083 &Cx1f; tad-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MEXICO-COFFEE-$ADV30-     05-27 1309
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MEXICO-COFFEE-$ADV30-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    IN A MEXICAN WAR ZONE, INDIANS FIGHT TO HARVEST ORGANIC COFFEE
