in hot pursuit of the bluefin tuna, an unusual fish that can be
sold in Tokyo for as much as $20,000 each.
</P>
<P>
   slugged: BC-JEWELS-OF-THE-SEA-NYTSF. Sent to category codes
``a'' general news and ``l'' lifestyle news.
