<P>
   COXNET TRAVEL 0525 -- For a first-time visitor, New York City
can be as intimidating as King Kong on a rampage down Fifth Avenue.
No wonder orchestrating a family getaway can be a daunting
prospect. There's so much to see and do in Manhattan, vacationers
find it hard to know where to start. (Crouch Thrasher, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) Art includes 4-column color photo of young
girl looking over the city from atop the Empire State Building.
