   GETAWAY _ Pensacola's Festival of Five Flags is June 2-12. We
visit beforehand and take readers on a tour of this historic town
with its museum, galleries, shops, restaurants and inns. (Thrasher,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 40. MOVED.
