<DOCNO> NYT19990527.0112 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-27 11:32 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3189 &Cx1f; tad-z
