<SLUG> BC-THIRTEENTH-FLOOR-REVIEW-LADN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
`THIRTEENTH FLOOR' A STEP BELOW `THE MATRIX'
</HEADLINE>
  F or use by NYTimes News Service clients)  
Our rating: 2 stars 
By GLENN WHIPP 
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ Coming as it does in the considerable wake of
