<SLUG> BC-NOTTINGHILL-REVIEW-LADN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
`NOTTING HILL' RISES ABOVE ROMANTIC PACK
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients)  
Our rating: 3 stars 
By BOB STRAUSS 
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ If, average guy, you have ever dreamed of Julia
Roberts falling in love with you, ``Notting Hill'' may give you
