<DOCNO> NYT19990527.0140 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-27 13:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3316 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SOC-REVOLUTION-BOS &LR;      05-27 0632
