<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-27 13:47 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3339 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SIERRA-CLUB-HNS &LR;      05-27 0625
