would lose transit funding in cutbacks approved by the Senate
Appropriations Committee. New York would lose $200 million and
California, $117 million, in the overall $12 billion measure. Rep.
John Sweeney, R-N.Y., and Sen. Dianne Feinstein, D-Calif., vow to
fight the cuts. By JENNIFER CORBETT DOOREN.
