extend trading hours _ and after several previous attempts failed
because of lack of interest among investors _ the nation's major
stock markets are now hurriedly readying plans to trade stocks for
several additional hours in the evening. On the horizon, many in
the industry see around-the-clock trading. A NASD announcement is
expected at 2 p.m. By Edward Wyatt.
</P>
