   TRAVEL-Q&AMP;A (Undated) _ Surface transportation in Hawaiian
waters; Stopping in Chartres; A choice of horse shows. By Paul
Freireich. (Moved).
</P>
<P>
   PRACTICAL-TRAVELER (Undated) _ Few assurances in trip insurance.
By Betsy Wade. (Moved).
</P>
