<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Where to find spoofs online
 &HT;    By Elizabeth Lee
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   Sites with ``Star Wars'' parodies or jokes:
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Countdown: The Ultimate Fan Site: www.countingdown.com
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Daily Sci-Fi's humor page: www.dailysci-fi.com/news/1251.html
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  The Force.net's humor page: www.theforce.net/humor
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Mos Eisley Multiplex's links to fan-made ``Star Wars'' films:
members.aol.com/moseisleym/sw-main.html
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Trooper Clerks (links to other sites where the video can be
downloaded): www.studiocreations.com/trooperclerks/
</P>
