<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
The Arizona Republic plans to move the following stories for use by
clients of
<TEXT>
<P>
   the NYTimes News Service for Friday, May 28. If you have any
questions, please call the Republic News Desk at (602) 444-8286.
